OL,3,CFive staff at Parc Prison sacked
OL,4,Cfollowing police investigation
OL,6,FFive members of staff have been sacked
OL,7,Ffrom Parc Prison in Bridgend following
OL,8,Fa police investigation into concerns
OL,9,Fover employee behaviour.
OL,11,FThe group had been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of assault and misconduct in
OL,13,Fpublic office in September 2024 and
OL,14,FJanuary 2025.
OL,16,FSouth Wales Police have confirmed all
OL,17,Fcriminal proceedings against those
OL,18,Farrested had now concluded, and all
OL,19,Fhave been released without charge.
