OL,3,CFive staff at Parc Prison sacked
OL,4,Cfollowing police investigation
OL,6,FIn statement, Detective Chief
OL,7,FInspector Dean Taylor said: "The
OL,8,Festablishment of a dedicated team by
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police to thoroughly
OL,10,Freview the allegations received
OL,11,Funderscores our commitment to
OL,12,Faccountability and integrity. This
OL,13,Fproactive approach not only addresses
OL,14,Fthe current concerns but also acts as
OL,15,Fa deterrent against future misconduct.
OL,17,F"I want to be clear that, together
OL,18,Fwith our partners at G4S, we are
OL,19,Ftaking significant steps to ensure
OL,20,Fthat inappropriate behaviour at HMP
OL,21,FParc will not be tolerated."
